briefTitle: Pilot 3D Mammography Reader Study to Assess Breast Cancer Detection in 3D Versus 2D Digital Mammography
officialTitle: A Multi-reader, Multi-case, Controlled Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Fuji Film 3D Digital Mammography System Used in Conjunction With 2D Digital Mammography in the Detection of Breast Cancer / A Pilot Study
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* Female subjects participating in prior FMSU protocol with known clinical status

Exclusion Criteria:

* Subjects with unkown clinical status
* Subjects not truthed in prior FMSU study
